ia Tabs</a> and <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="external underline">WordPress Social Network Tabs</a> now includes the Instagram API, bringing the total number of supported networks to 17 with 49 feed options!</p>\n<h3>Instagram Tab Feed Options</h3>\n<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_api_feed_tab.jpg" alt="Instagram Feed Tab" class="img-right hide-excerpt" /></p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Show an Instagram user feed</li>\n<li>Search Instagram tags</li>\n<li>Show an Instagram Location ID feed</li>\n<li>Search by latitude/longitude + distance</li>\n<li>Show post likes with user thumbnail avatar</li>\n<li>Show latest comments</li>\n<li>Select image size &#8211; 306 px, 150 px or 612 px</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In addition to the Instagram update the plugin now includes the ability to display twitter search feeds and options to disable both retweets and twitter replies.</p>\n<h3>View The Plugin Demos</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="underline">Social Network Tabs for WordPress</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Purchase From Codecanyon</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-media-tabs/1932796?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/social-network-tabs-for-wordpress/1982987?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">Social Network Tabs for WordPress</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/sr4nKXO7Jj4" height="1" width="1"/>";}i:7;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:63:"New Premium WordPress Plugin – WordPress Social Share Buttons";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DesignChemical/~3/-IfzAm-IASc/";s:8:"comments";s:132:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/new-premium-wordpress-plugin-wordpress-social-share-buttons/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Fri, 31 Aug 2012 09:45:17 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:5:"Admin";}s:8:"category";s:128:"Wordpress Pluginsdeliciousdiggemailfacebookgoogle +1jQuerylinkedinpinterestpluginssocial networksstumbleupontwitterwordpressxing";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/?p=3580";s:11:"description";s:738:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/wordpress_social_share_buttons.png" alt="WordPress Social Share Buttons Plugin" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Our latest premium WordPress plugin is a WordPress implementation of our successful jQuery Social Share Buttons plugin.</p>\n<p>The plugin adds jQuery social share buttons to WordPress in a stylish floating panel, toolbar or display inline. The plugin supports 10 social network share buttons + bonus print &#038; email buttons.</p>\n<p>For more information and plugin demos go to the WordPress Social  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/new-premium-wordpress-plugin-wordpress-social-share-buttons/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:3932:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/wordpress_social_share_buttons.png" alt="WordPress Social Share Buttons Plugin" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Our latest premium WordPress plugin is a WordPress implementation of our successful <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Share Buttons plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>The plugin adds jQuery social share buttons to WordPress in a stylish floating panel, toolbar or display inline. The plugin supports 10 social network share buttons + bonus print &#038; email buttons.</p>\n<p>For more information and plugin demos go to the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/wordpress-social-share-buttons/" class="underline">WordPress Social Share Buttons Demo Site</a> or download via <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/wordpress-social-share-buttons/2927356?ref=designchemical" class="underline">codecanyon</a>.</p>\n<h3>Supported Social Networks</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Twitter</li>\n<li>Facebook</li>\n<li>Google +1</li>\n<li>LinkedIn</li>\n<li>Delicious</li>\n<li>Digg</li>\n<li>Pinterest</li>\n<li>Stumbleupon</li>\n<li>Buffer</li>\n<li>Xing</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Check Out Our Full Range of Premium WordPress &#038; Jq