dPress plugin is a WordPress implementation of our successful <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Share Buttons plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>The plugin adds jQuery social share buttons to WordPress in a stylish floating panel, toolbar or display inline. The plugin supports 10 social network share buttons + bonus print &#038; email buttons.</p>\n<p>For more information and plugin demos go to the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/wordpress-social-share-buttons/" class="underline">WordPress Social Share Buttons Demo Site</a> or download via <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/wordpress-social-share-buttons/2927356?ref=designchemical" class="underline">codecanyon</a>.</p>\n<h3>Supported Social Networks</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Twitter</li>\n<li>Facebook</li>\n<li>Google +1</li>\n<li>LinkedIn</li>\n<li>Delicious</li>\n<li>Digg</li>\n<li>Pinterest</li>\n<li>Stumbleupon</li>\n<li>Buffer</li>\n<li>Xing</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Check Out Our Full Range of Premium WordPress &#038; Jquery Plugins:</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a class="external" href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/wordpress-social-stream-plugin/">WordPress Social Stream</a></li>\n<li><a class="external" href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/">WordPress Social Network Tabs</a></li>\n<li><a class="external" href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/wordpress-social-share-buttons/">WordPress Social Share Buttons</a></li>\n<li><a class="external" href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-top-social-share-posts/">WordPress Top Social Share Posts</a></li>\n<li><a class="external" href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></li>\n<li><a class="external" href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/">jQuery Social Share Buttons</a></li>\n<li><a class="external" href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/">jQuery Social Stream</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-IfzAm-IASc:KC_QlmQpBc8:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-IfzAm-IASc:KC_QlmQpBc8:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-IfzAm-IASc:KC_QlmQpBc8:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-IfzAm-IASc:KC_QlmQpBc8:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-IfzAm-IASc:KC_QlmQpBc8:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-IfzAm-IASc:KC_QlmQpBc8:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-IfzAm-IASc:KC_QlmQpBc8:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-IfzAm-IASc:KC_QlmQpBc8:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-IfzAm-IASc:KC_QlmQpBc8:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-IfzAm-IASc:KC_QlmQpBc8:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/-IfzAm-IASc" height="1" width="1"/>";}i:8;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:59:"Instagram Added To jQuery & WordPress Social Stream Plugins";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DesignChemical/~3/ZGw6kDIXaKo/";s:8:"comments";s:130:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/instagram-added-to-jquery-wordpress-social-stream-plugins/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Fri, 24 Aug 2012 10:00:02 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:5:"Admin";}s:8:"category";s:75:"Wordpress PluginsinstagramjQuerypluginssocial mediasocial networkswordpress";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/?p=3503";s:11:"description";s:922:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_social_stream_wall.jpg" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Version 1.4 of jQuery Social Stream and WordPress Social Stream now includes the Instagram network. With the addition of the Instagram API both plugins now support a total of 15 social networks with 37 feed options!</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_api_feed.jpg" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-right hide-excerpt" /></p>\nInstagram Feed Options\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Show an Instagram user feed</li>\n<li>Search Instagram tags</li>\n<li>Show an Instagram Location ID feed</li>\n<li>Search by latitude/longitude + distance</li>\n<li>Show post </li> &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/instagram-added-to-jquery-wordpress-social-stream-plugins/" class="read_more">more</a></ul>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:3692:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_social_stream_wall.jpg" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Version 1.4 of <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">jQuery Social Stream</a> and <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/wordpress-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">WordPress Social Stream</a> now includes the Instagram network. With the addition of the Instagram API both plugins now support a total of 15 social networks with 37 feed options!</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_api_feed.jpg" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-right hide-excerpt" /></p>\n<h3>Instagram Feed Options</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Show an Instagram user feed</li>\n<li>Search Instagram tags</li>\n<li>Show an Instagram Location ID feed</li>\n<li>Search by latitude/longitude + distance</li>\n<li>Show post likes with user thumbnail avatar</li>\n<li>Show latest comments</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The jQuery Social Stream plugin and the WordPress version can handle multiple Instagram searches and feeds in a single stream.</p>\n<p>Display your streams as a rotating feed widget or a jQuery isotope network wall &#8211; see demo of <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/social-network-stream-wall-with-instagram-search/" class="underline">social network wall showing Instagram search + user feed</a>.</p>\n<h3>View The Plugin Demos</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">jQuery Social Stream</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/wordpress-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">WordPress Social Stream</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Purchase From Codecanyon</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-stream/2103997?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">jQuery Social Stream</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/wordpress-social-stream/2201708?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">WordPress Social Stream</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/ZGw6kDIXaKo" height="1" width="1"/>";}s:3:"wfw";a:1:{s:10:"commentrss";s:126:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/instagram-added-to-jquery-wordpress-social-stream-plugins/feed/";}s:5:"slash";a:1:{s:8:"comments";s:1:"0";}s:10:"feedburner";a:1:{s:8:"origlink";s:121:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/instagram-added-to-jquery-wordpress-social-stream-plugins/";}s:7:"summary";s:922:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_social_stream_wall.jpg" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Version 1.4 of jQuery Social Stream and WordPress Social Stream now includes the Instagram network. With the addition of the Instagram API both plugins now support a total of 15 social networks with 37 feed options!</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_api_feed.jpg" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-right hide-excerpt" /></p>\nInstagram Feed Options\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Show an Instagram user feed</li>\n<li>Search Instagram tags</li>\n<li>Show an Instagram Location ID feed</li>\n<li>Search by latitude/longitude + distance</li>\n<li>Show post </li> &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/instagram-added-to-jquery-wordpress-social-stream-plugins/" class="read_more">more</a></ul>";s:12:"atom_content";s:3692:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_social_stream_wall.jpg" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Version 1.4 of <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">jQuery Social Stream</a> and <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/wordpress-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">WordPress Social Stream</a> now includes the Instagram network. With the addition of the Instagram API both plugins now support a total of 15 social networks with 37 feed options!</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_api_feed.jpg" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-right hide-excerpt" /></p>\n<h3>Instagram Feed Options</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Show an Instagram user feed</li>\n<li>Search Instagram tags</li>\n<li>Show an Instagram Location ID feed</li>\n<li>Search by latitude/longitude + distance</li>\n<li>Show post likes with user thumbnail avatar</li>\n<li>Show latest comments</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The jQuery Social Stream plugin and the WordPress version can handle multiple Instagram searches and feeds in a single stream.</p>\n<p>Display your streams as a rotating feed widget or a jQuery isotope network wall &#8211; see demo of <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/social-network-stream-wall-with-instagram-search/" class="underline">social network wall showing Instagram search + user feed</a>.</p>\n<h3>View The Plugin Demos</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">jQuery Social Stream</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/wordpress-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">WordPress Social Stream</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Purchase From Codecanyon</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-stream/2103997?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">jQuery Social Stream</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/wordpress-social-stream/2201708?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">WordPress Social Stream</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=ZGw6kDIXaKo:HU4YgQafzW4:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/ZGw6kDIXaKo" height="1" width="1"/>";}i:9;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:61:"Xing Share Button Added To jQuery Social Share Buttons Plugin";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DesignChemical/~3/-7bF1X1WpwU/";s:8:"comments";s:131:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/xing-share-button-added-to-jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Mon, 06 Aug 2012 10:57:10 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:5:"Admin";}s:8:"category";s:46:"jQuery PluginsjQuerypluginssocial networksxing";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/?p=3476";s:11:"description";s:820:"<p class="text-center pad-top"><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/xing_button.png" alt="Xing Share Button" /></p>\n<p>Xing social share button is now included in our popular jQuery Social Share Buttons Plugin. The Xing button is available in 3 sizes &#8211; vertical with count, horizontal with count and horizontal with no count.</p>\n<p class="text-center"><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/xing_buttons.png" alt="Xing Social Share Button" /></p>\nXing Hovercard Statistics\n<p>Xing also offer an extra feature with their share buttons &#8211; a hovercard, which shows the popularity of your website content with  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/xing-share-button-added-to-jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:3103:"<p class="text-center pad-top"><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/xing_button.png" alt="Xing Share Button" /></p>\n<p>Xing social share button is now included in our popular <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/">jQuery Social Share Buttons Plugin</a>. The Xing button is available in 3 sizes &#8211; vertical with count, horizontal with count and horizontal with no count.</p>\n<p class="text-center"><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/xing_buttons.png" alt="Xing Social Share Button" /></p>\n<h3>Xing Hovercard Statistics</h3>\n<p>Xing also offer an extra feature with their share buttons &#8211; a hovercard, which shows the popularity of your website content with additional statistics such as the total number of clicks, likes and comments for the link on XING.</p>\n<p>The <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/">jQuery Social Share Buttons Plugin</a> now includes 10 social network share buttons:</p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Twitter</li>\n<li>Facebook</li>\n<li>Google +1</li>\n<li>LinkedIn</li>\n<li>Delicious</li>\n<li>Digg</li>\n<li>Pinterest</li>\n<li>Stumbleupon</li>\n<li>Buffer</li>\n<li>Xing</li>\n<li>Print Button</li>\n<li>Email Button</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For more information go to the plugin demo site &#8211; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/" class="underline external">jQuery Social Share Buttons Plugin</a> or purchase directly from <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/1742435?ref=designchemical" class="underline external">Codeanyon</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/-7bF1X1WpwU" height="1" width="1"/>";}s:3:"wfw";a:1:{s:10:"commentrss";s:127:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/xing-share-button-added-to-jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/feed/";}s:5:"slash";a:1:{s:8:"comments";s:1:"0";}s:10:"feedburner";a:1:{s:8:"origlink";s:122:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/xing-share-button-added-to-jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/";}s:7:"summary";s:820:"<p class="text-center pad-top"><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/xing_button.png" alt="Xing Share Button" /></p>\n<p>Xing social share button is now included in our popular jQuery Social Share Buttons Plugin. The Xing button is available in 3 sizes &#8211; vertical with count, horizontal with count and horizontal with no count.</p>\n<p class="text-center"><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/xing_buttons.png" alt="Xing Social Share Button" /></p>\nXing Hovercard Statistics\n<p>Xing also offer an extra feature with their share buttons &#8211; a hovercard, which shows the popularity of your website content with  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/xing-share-button-added-to-jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:12:"atom_content";s:3103:"<p class="text-center pad-top"><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/xing_button.png" alt="Xing Share Button" /></p>\n<p>Xing social share button is now included in our popular <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/">jQuery Social Share Buttons Plugin</a>. The Xing button is available in 3 sizes &#8211; vertical with count, horizontal with count and horizontal with no count.</p>\n<p class="text-center"><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/xing_buttons.png" alt="Xing Social Share Button" /></p>\n<h3>Xing Hovercard Statistics</h3>\n<p>Xing also offer an extra feature with their share buttons &#8211; a hovercard, which shows the popularity of your website content with additional statistics such as the total number of clicks, likes and comments for the link on XING.</p>\n<p>The <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/">jQuery Social Share Buttons Plugin</a> now includes 10 social network share buttons:</p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Twitter</li>\n<li>Facebook</li>\n<li>Google +1</li>\n<li>LinkedIn</li>\n<li>Delicious</li>\n<li>Digg</li>\n<li>Pinterest</li>\n<li>Stumbleupon</li>\n<li>Buffer</li>\n<li>Xing</li>\n<li>Print Button</li>\n<li>Email Button</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For more information go to the plugin demo site &#8211; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/" class="underline external">jQuery Social Share Buttons Plugin</a> or purchase directly from <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-share-buttons-plugin/1742435?ref=designchemical" class="underline external">Codeanyon</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=-7bF1X1WpwU:FxYEE1HUxK8:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/-7bF1X1WpwU" height="1" width="1"/>";}i:10;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:82:"LinkedIn Added To jQuery Social Media Tabs & WordPress Social Network Tabs Plugins";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DesignChemical/~3/F7Tqa-V8JMM/";s:8:"comments";s:153:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/linkedin-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-wordpress-social-network-tabs-plugins/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Mon, 18 Jun 2012 07:02:30 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:5:"Admin";}s:8:"category";s:62:"Wordpress PluginsjQuerylinkedinpluginssocial networkswordpress";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/?p=3440";s:11:"description";s:686:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/linkedin_plugins.png" alt="LinkedIn Plugins" class="" /></p>\n<p>Version 1.5 of both the jQuery Social Media Tabs plugin and the WordPress Social Network Tabs plugin now include the option to add a LinkedIn tab showing up to 4 LinkedIn plugins:</p>\nMember Profile Plugin\n<p>A personal profile widget displaying your LinkedIn profile image, name, current position, location plus a link to your main profile page. Also includes the option  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/linkedin-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-wordpress-social-network-tabs-plugins/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:3273:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/linkedin_plugins.png" alt="LinkedIn Plugins" class="" /></p>\n<p>Version 1.5 of both the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a> plugin and the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="underline">WordPress Social Network Tabs</a> plugin now include the option to add a LinkedIn tab showing up to 4 LinkedIn plugins:</p>\n<h3>Member Profile Plugin</h3>\n<p>A personal profile widget displaying your LinkedIn profile image, name, current position, location plus a link to your main profile page. Also includes the option to show links to related profiles.</p>\n<h3>Company Profile Plugin</h3>\n<p>A company profile widget showing the company name, logo, summary text and &#8220;follow&#8221; button with an additional option to show company employees in the viewers network.</p>\n<h3>Company Insider Plugin</h3>\n<p>A more detailed company plugin, which includes tabs to show employees in the viewers network, new hires and promotions/changes.</p>\n<h3>Jobs You May Be Interested In</h3>\n<p>A widget showing a list of jobs that may be interesting to a viewer &#8211; this can be set to either show jobs from a specific company or a general list from the linkedin network.</p>\n<p>The latest versions of the plugins, which support 16 social networks with a total of 41 different feed options are now available for download at codecanyon:</p>\n<p><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-media-tabs/1932796?ref=designchemical" class="underline external">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/social-network-tabs-for-wordpress/1982987?ref=designchemical" class="underline external">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/F7Tqa-V8JMM" height="1" width="1"/>";}s:3:"wfw";a:1:{s:10:"commentrss";s:149:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/linkedin-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-wordpress-social-network-tabs-plugins/feed/";}s:5:"slash";a:1:{s:8:"comments";s:1:"2";}s:10:"feedburner";a:1:{s:8:"origlink";s:144:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/linkedin-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-wordpress-social-network-tabs-plugins/";}s:7:"summary";s:686:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/linkedin_plugins.png" alt="LinkedIn Plugins" class="" /></p>\n<p>Version 1.5 of both the jQuery Social Media Tabs plugin and the WordPress Social Network Tabs plugin now include the option to add a LinkedIn tab showing up to 4 LinkedIn plugins:</p>\nMember Profile Plugin\n<p>A personal profile widget displaying your LinkedIn profile image, name, current position, location plus a link to your main profile page. Also includes the option  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/linkedin-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-wordpress-social-network-tabs-plugins/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:12:"atom_content";s:3273:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/linkedin_plugins.png" alt="LinkedIn Plugins" class="" /></p>\n<p>Version 1.5 of both the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a> plugin and the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="underline">WordPress Social Network Tabs</a> plugin now include the option to add a LinkedIn tab showing up to 4 LinkedIn plugins:</p>\n<h3>Member Profile Plugin</h3>\n<p>A personal profile widget displaying your LinkedIn profile image, name, current position, location plus a link to your main profile page. Also includes the option to show links to related profiles.</p>\n<h3>Company Profile Plugin</h3>\n<p>A company profile widget showing the company name, logo, summary text and &#8220;follow&#8221; button with an additional option to show company employees in the viewers network.</p>\n<h3>Company Insider Plugin</h3>\n<p>A more detailed company plugin, which includes tabs to show employees in the viewers network, new hires and promotions/changes.</p>\n<h3>Jobs You May Be Interested In</h3>\n<p>A widget showing a list of jobs that may be interesting to a viewer &#8211; this can be set to either show jobs from a specific company or a general list from the linkedin network.</p>\n<p>The latest versions of the plugins, which support 16 social networks with a total of 41 different feed options are now available for download at codecanyon:</p>\n<p><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-media-tabs/1932796?ref=designchemical" class="underline external">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/social-network-tabs-for-wordpress/1982987?ref=designchemical" class="underline external">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=F7Tqa-V8JMM:EA_Fqeuk_m8:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/F7Tqa-V8JMM" height="1" width="1"/>";}i:11;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:60:"Tumblr & Deviantart Added To jQuery Social Media Tabs Plugin";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DesignChemical/~3/bZc0NnOC_hE/";s:8:"comments";s:131:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/tumblr-deviantart-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Mon, 28 May 2012 04:48:26 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:5:"Admin";}s:8:"category";s:70:"Wordpress PluginsdeviantartjQuerypluginssocial networkstumblrwordpress";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/?p=3408";s:11:"description";s:581:"<p>Starting with versions 1.4 both the jQuery Social Media Tabs &#038; the Social Network Tabs For WordPress plugins now include Tumblr and Deviantart tabs giving a total of 15 social networks supported with 33 different feed options.</p>\n<p>The Tumblr feed includes specific styling and formatting for all tumblr content types &#8211; photo, video, regular, quote, audio, conversation &#038; link, including  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/tumblr-deviantart-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:3247:"<p>Starting with versions 1.4 both the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a> &#038; the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="underline">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a> plugins now include Tumblr and Deviantart tabs giving a total of 15 social networks supported with 33 different feed options.</p>\n<p>The Tumblr feed includes specific styling and formatting for all tumblr content types &#8211; photo, video, regular, quote, audio, conversation &#038; link, including an inline video player for video posts and options for setting thumbnail and video player width.</p>\n<p>Other updates to both plugins include:</p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Added option to show tweets from a twitter list</li>\n<li>Option to display twitter profile avatar image in each tweet</li>\n<li>Option to display complete text &#038; images for both facebook and RSS feed posts</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Latest versions now available from codecanyon</p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/social-network-tabs-for-wordpress/1982987?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-media-tabs/1932796" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Plugin Demo Sites</h3>\n<p><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="underline">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/bZc0NnOC_hE" height="1" width="1"/>";}s:3:"wfw";a:1:{s:10:"commentrss";s:127:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/tumblr-deviantart-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/feed/";}s:5:"slash";a:1:{s:8:"comments";s:1:"0";}s:10:"feedburner";a:1:{s:8:"origlink";s:122:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/tumblr-deviantart-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/";}s:7:"summary";s:581:"<p>Starting with versions 1.4 both the jQuery Social Media Tabs &#038; the Social Network Tabs For WordPress plugins now include Tumblr and Deviantart tabs giving a total of 15 social networks supported with 33 different feed options.</p>\n<p>The Tumblr feed includes specific styling and formatting for all tumblr content types &#8211; photo, video, regular, quote, audio, conversation &#038; link, including  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/tumblr-deviantart-added-to-jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:12:"atom_content";s:3247:"<p>Starting with versions 1.4 both the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a> &#038; the <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="underline">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a> plugins now include Tumblr and Deviantart tabs giving a total of 15 social networks supported with 33 different feed options.</p>\n<p>The Tumblr feed includes specific styling and formatting for all tumblr content types &#8211; photo, video, regular, quote, audio, conversation &#038; link, including an inline video player for video posts and options for setting thumbnail and video player width.</p>\n<p>Other updates to both plugins include:</p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Added option to show tweets from a twitter list</li>\n<li>Option to display twitter profile avatar image in each tweet</li>\n<li>Option to display complete text &#038; images for both facebook and RSS feed posts</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Latest versions now available from codecanyon</p>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/social-network-tabs-for-wordpress/1982987?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-media-tabs/1932796" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Plugin Demo Sites</h3>\n<p><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/" class="underline">Social Network Tabs For WordPress</a></p>\n<p><a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=bZc0NnOC_hE:9bf-k_mfJdo:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/bZc0NnOC_hE" height="1" width="1"/>";}i:12;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:47:"jQuery Social Stream Plugin Now Includes Tumblr";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DesignChemical/~3/H5pZl1FpcSs/";s:8:"comments";s:117:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin-now-includes-tumblr/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Thu, 26 Apr 2012 01:19:38 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:5:"Admin";}s:8:"category";s:48:"jQuery PluginsjQuerypluginssocial networkstumblr";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/?p=3371";s:11:"description";s:687:"<p><img src="/media/images/jquery_social_stream_wall.png" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Starting version 1.2 our popular premium jQuery plugin, jQuery Social Stream, now includes the Tumblr network, bringing the total number of supported networks to 14 with 26 different feed options.</p>\n<p>The Tumblr feed includes specific styling and formatting for all tumblr content types &#8211; photo, video, regular, quote, audio, conversation &#038; link, including an inline video player for video posts. &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin-now-includes-tumblr/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:2562:"<p><img src="/media/images/jquery_social_stream_wall.png" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Starting version 1.2 our popular premium jQuery plugin, jQuery Social Stream, now includes the Tumblr network, bringing the total number of supported networks to 14 with 26 different feed options.</p>\n<p>The Tumblr feed includes specific styling and formatting for all tumblr content types &#8211; photo, video, regular, quote, audio, conversation &#038; link, including an inline video player for video posts.</p>\n<p>Options for the tumblr feed include set thumbnail width, video player width as well as being able to control the feed item content.</p>\n<p>jQuery Social Stream can handle multiple, unlimited tumblr profiles in a single stream or create multiple streams per page. Streams can be displayed as a rotating feed widget or a jQuery isotope network wall.</p>\n<p>Tumblr version now available from <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-stream/2103997?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">codecanyon</a> or view the <a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">live demo site</a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/H5pZl1FpcSs" height="1" width="1"/>";}s:3:"wfw";a:1:{s:10:"commentrss";s:113:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin-now-includes-tumblr/feed/";}s:5:"slash";a:1:{s:8:"comments";s:1:"2";}s:10:"feedburner";a:1:{s:8:"origlink";s:108:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin-now-includes-tumblr/";}s:7:"summary";s:687:"<p><img src="/media/images/jquery_social_stream_wall.png" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Starting version 1.2 our popular premium jQuery plugin, jQuery Social Stream, now includes the Tumblr network, bringing the total number of supported networks to 14 with 26 different feed options.</p>\n<p>The Tumblr feed includes specific styling and formatting for all tumblr content types &#8211; photo, video, regular, quote, audio, conversation &#038; link, including an inline video player for video posts. &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin-now-includes-tumblr/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:12:"atom_content";s:2562:"<p><img src="/media/images/jquery_social_stream_wall.png" alt="jQuery Social Stream Wall" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Starting version 1.2 our popular premium jQuery plugin, jQuery Social Stream, now includes the Tumblr network, bringing the total number of supported networks to 14 with 26 different feed options.</p>\n<p>The Tumblr feed includes specific styling and formatting for all tumblr content types &#8211; photo, video, regular, quote, audio, conversation &#038; link, including an inline video player for video posts.</p>\n<p>Options for the tumblr feed include set thumbnail width, video player width as well as being able to control the feed item content.</p>\n<p>jQuery Social Stream can handle multiple, unlimited tumblr profiles in a single stream or create multiple streams per page. Streams can be displayed as a rotating feed widget or a jQuery isotope network wall.</p>\n<p>Tumblr version now available from <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-stream/2103997?ref=designchemical" rel="nofollow" class="external underline">codecanyon</a> or view the <a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">live demo site</a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=H5pZl1FpcSs:KH0U_ZbsdGw:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/H5pZl1FpcSs" height="1" width="1"/>";}i:13;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:52:"Premium WordPress Plugin – WordPress Social Stream";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DesignChemical/~3/gMRTCHxwjBs/";s:8:"comments";s:121:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-wordpress-social-stream/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Fri, 20 Apr 2012 04:10:45 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:5:"Admin";}s:8:"category";s:117:"Wordpress Pluginsfacebookgoogle +1isotopejQuerylast.fmpinterestsocial networksstumbleupontwittervimeowordpressYouTube";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/?p=3347";s:11:"description";s:570:"<p>The latest premium WordPress plugin is a WordPress implementation of our recent, successful jQuery Social Stream plugin.</p>\n<p>Go to WordPress Social Stream Demo Site</p>\n<p>Combine all of your social network interactions into one single network stream or create a single feed for multiple social network profiles. Display using a filterable jQuery isotope powered Social Network Wall or a rotating feed  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-wordpress-social-stream/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:2865:"<p>The latest premium WordPress plugin is a WordPress implementation of our recent, successful <a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/">jQuery Social Stream plugin</a>.</p>\n<p><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/wordpress-social-stream-plugin/">Go to WordPress Social Stream Demo Site</a></p>\n<p>Combine all of your social network interactions into one single network stream or create a single feed for multiple social network profiles. Display using a filterable jQuery isotope powered Social Network Wall or a rotating feed list!</p>\n<h3>Includes 13 social networks &#038; 25 feed options:</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Twitter &#8211; Latest Tweets</li>\n<li>Facebook &#8211; Page Latest Wall Posts</li>\n<li>Google +1 &#8211; +1 Latest Posts</li>\n<li>RSS Feed &#8211; Latest Posts</li>\n<li>Delicious &#8211; Latest Likes</li>\n<li>Stumbleupon &#8211; Favorites or Reviews</li>\n<li>Pinterest &#8211; Latest Pins</li>\n<li>Dribbble &#8211; Latest Shots or Likes</li>\n<li>Youtube &#8211; Latest Uploads, Favorites or new subscription videos</li>\n<li>Vimeo &#8211; Likes, Videos, Appeared In, Albums, Channels or Groups</li>\n<li>Flickr &#8211; Latest Uploads</li>\n<li>last.fm &#8211; Loved Tracks, Recent Tracks or Reply Tracker</li>\n<li>Deviantart &#8211; Latest Deviations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out our full range of premium WordPress and Jquery plugins at <a href="http://codecanyon.net/user/designchemical/portfolio?ref=designchemical">codecanyon</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/gMRTCHxwjBs" height="1" width="1"/>";}s:3:"wfw";a:1:{s:10:"commentrss";s:117:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-wordpress-social-stream/feed/";}s:5:"slash";a:1:{s:8:"comments";s:1:"4";}s:10:"feedburner";a:1:{s:8:"origlink";s:112:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-wordpress-social-stream/";}s:7:"summary";s:570:"<p>The latest premium WordPress plugin is a WordPress implementation of our recent, successful jQuery Social Stream plugin.</p>\n<p>Go to WordPress Social Stream Demo Site</p>\n<p>Combine all of your social network interactions into one single network stream or create a single feed for multiple social network profiles. Display using a filterable jQuery isotope powered Social Network Wall or a rotating feed  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-wordpress-social-stream/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:12:"atom_content";s:2865:"<p>The latest premium WordPress plugin is a WordPress implementation of our recent, successful <a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/">jQuery Social Stream plugin</a>.</p>\n<p><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/wordpress-social-stream-plugin/">Go to WordPress Social Stream Demo Site</a></p>\n<p>Combine all of your social network interactions into one single network stream or create a single feed for multiple social network profiles. Display using a filterable jQuery isotope powered Social Network Wall or a rotating feed list!</p>\n<h3>Includes 13 social networks &#038; 25 feed options:</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Twitter &#8211; Latest Tweets</li>\n<li>Facebook &#8211; Page Latest Wall Posts</li>\n<li>Google +1 &#8211; +1 Latest Posts</li>\n<li>RSS Feed &#8211; Latest Posts</li>\n<li>Delicious &#8211; Latest Likes</li>\n<li>Stumbleupon &#8211; Favorites or Reviews</li>\n<li>Pinterest &#8211; Latest Pins</li>\n<li>Dribbble &#8211; Latest Shots or Likes</li>\n<li>Youtube &#8211; Latest Uploads, Favorites or new subscription videos</li>\n<li>Vimeo &#8211; Likes, Videos, Appeared In, Albums, Channels or Groups</li>\n<li>Flickr &#8211; Latest Uploads</li>\n<li>last.fm &#8211; Loved Tracks, Recent Tracks or Reply Tracker</li>\n<li>Deviantart &#8211; Latest Deviations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out our full range of premium WordPress and Jquery plugins at <a href="http://codecanyon.net/user/designchemical/portfolio?ref=designchemical">codecanyon</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:-BTjWOF_DHI"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=gMRTCHxwjBs:ogC55Ssinz4:-BTjWOF_DHI" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/gMRTCHxwjBs" height="1" width="1"/>";}i:14;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:50:"New Premium jQuery Plugin – jQuery Social Stream";s:4:"link";s:61:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/DesignChemical/~3/2WgnTYP6GqU/";s:8:"comments";s:116:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/new-premium-jquery-plugin-jquery-social-stream/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Thu, 12 Apr 2012 03:59:00 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:5:"Admin";}s:8:"category";s:126:"jQuery PluginsAJAXdeliciousdeviantartfacebookgoogle +1jQuerylast.fmpinterestpluginsrsssocial networksstumbleupontwitterYouTube";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/?p=3258";s:11:"description";s:682:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/jquery_social_stream.jpg" alt="jQuery Social Stream" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Combine all of your social network interactions into a single network stream or create a single feed for multiple social network profiles. Includes 13 social networks with a total of 24 different feed options.</p>\n<p>Using only jQuery, the social stream plugin can be used for ANY website &#8230; including WordPress &#8230; no PHP required!</p>\n<p>View jQuery Social Stream Plugin Demo  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/new-premium-jquery-plugin-jquery-social-stream/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:4938:"<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/jquery_social_stream.jpg" alt="jQuery Social Stream" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Combine all of your social network interactions into a single network stream or create a single feed for multiple social network profiles. Includes 13 social networks with a total of 24 different feed options.</p>\n<p>Using only jQuery, the social stream plugin can be used for ANY website &#8230; including WordPress &#8230; no PHP required!</p>\n<p><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/" class="external underline">View jQuery Social Stream Plugin Demo Site</a></p>\n<h3>Plugin Supports 13 Social Networks</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Twitter &#8211; Latest Tweets</li>\n<li>Facebook &#8211; Page Latest Wall Posts</li>\n<li>Google +1 &#8211; Latest +1 Posts</li>\n<li>RSS Feed &#8211; Latest Posts</li>\n<li>Delicious &#8211; Latest Likes</li>\n<li>Stumbleupon &#8211; Favorites or Reviews</li>\n<li>Pinterest &#8211; Latest Pins</li>\n<li>Dribbble &#8211; Latest Shots or Likes</li>\n<li>Youtube &#8211; Latest Uploads or Favorites</li>\n<li>Vimeo &#8211; Likes, Videos, Appeared In, Albums, Channels or Groups</li>\n<li>Flickr &#8211; Latest Uploads</li>\n<li>last.fm &#8211; Loved Tracks, Recent Tracks or Reply Tracker</li>\n<li>Deviantart &#8211; Latest Deviations</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Social Stream Display Options</h3>\n<p>Display using rotating feed list or a filterable jQuery Isotope powered Social Network Wall!</p>\n<div style="float: left;">\n<p><strong>Includes 2 sample skins for the rotating list:</strong></p>\n<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/dcsns_feed.png" alt="jQuery Social Stream Feed" class="img-border" /></div>\n<div style="float: right;">\n<p><strong>Pinterest style Social Network Wall:</strong></p>\n<p><img src="http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/dcsns_wall.png" alt="jQuery Social Stream Network Wall" class="img-border" /></div>\n<p class="clear">Options include setting the stream to display items by date based on total number of days or number of latest feed items from each network.</p>\n<h3>jQuery Social Media Tabs Plugin Demos</h3>\n<p>Check out the <a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/" class="underline">plugin home page</a> for more details or view the social stream demos:</p>\n<div class="banner-horizontal float-right">\n<script type="text/javascript"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = "ca-pub-7740611438413740";\n/* Link Mid Content */\ngoogle_ad_slot = "2373698085";\ngoogle_ad_width = 200;\ngoogle_ad_height = 90;\n//-->\n</script><br />\n<script type="text/javascript"\nsrc="http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js">\n</script>\n</div>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin-quickstart-demo/">Quickstart</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin-light-skin/">Quickstart &#8211; Light Skin</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin-multiple-profiles-demo/">Using Multiple Profiles</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin-custom-output-demo/">Custom Output</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin-creating-a-network-wall/">Social Network Wall</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>jQuery Social Stream Plugin is now available from <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-stream/2103997?ref=designchemical" class="external underline" rel="nofollow">codecanyon</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=2WgnTYP6GqU:Z0TCcI0AtFI:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=2WgnTYP6GqU:Z0TCcI0AtFI:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=2WgnTYP6GqU:Z0TCcI0AtFI:F7zBnMyn0Lo"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=2WgnTYP6GqU:Z0TCcI0AtFI:F7zBnMyn0Lo" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.fe