 a total of 30 different feed options &#8211; Combine all of your favorite social networks profiles &#038; feeds into slick slide out or static tabs.</p>\n<p>jQuery Social Media Tabs gives similar functionality to our WordPress Social Media Tabs Plugin but with even more social networks and can be added to ANY website &#8230; including WordPress  &#8230; <a href="http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/new-premium-jquery-plugin-social-media-tabs/" class="read_more">more</a></p>";s:7:"content";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";s:4725:"<p><img src="/media/images/jquery_social_media_tabs.png" alt="jQuery Social Share Buttons" class="img-border" /></p>\n<p>Includes 13 social networks with a total of 30 different feed options &#8211; Combine all of your favorite social networks profiles &#038; feeds into slick slide out or static tabs.</p>\n<p>jQuery Social Media Tabs gives similar functionality to our WordPress Social Media Tabs Plugin but with even more social networks and can be added to ANY website &#8230; including WordPress &#8230; no PHP required!</p>\n<p><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="external underline">Go To jQuery Social Media Tabs Demo Site</a></p>\n<h3>Plugin Supports 13 Social Networks</h3>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li>Twitter &#8211; Latest Tweets</li>\n<li>Facebook &#8211; Wall Posts</li>\n<li>Facebook &#8211; Like Box</li>\n<li>Facebook &#8211; Recommendations</li>\n<li>Google +1 &#8211; Latest google profile +1</li>\n<li>RSS Feed &#8211; Latest Posts</li>\n<li>Delicious &#8211; Latest Likes</li>\n<li>Digg &#8211; Latest Diggs</li>\n<li>Pinterest &#8211; Latest Pins</li>\n<li>Youtube &#8211; Latest Uploads or Favorites</li>\n<li>Flickr &#8211; Latest Uploads</li>\n<li>last.fm &#8211; Loved Tracks, Recent Tracks or Reply Tracker</li>\n<li>dribbble &#8211; Latest shots &#038; Likes</li>\n<li>Vimeo &#8211; Likes, Videos, Appeared In, Albums, Channels &#038; Groups</li>\n<li>Stumbleupon &#8211; Favorites or Reviews</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Each social network tab loaded using AJAX only when required making the plugin very fast loading! Also includes option for auto or manual ticker style rotating content for each social network feed, which gives you unlimited capacity for listing your feed items.</p>\n<h3>jQuery Social Media Tabs Plugin Demos</h3>\n<p>Check out the <a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/" class="underline">plugin home page</a> for more details or view the social media tabs demos, include the configurable <a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin-example-2/">&#8220;Create your own demo&#8221;</a>:</p>\n<div class="banner-horizontal float-right">\n<script type="text/javascript"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = "ca-pub-7740611438413740";\n/* Link Mid Content */\ngoogle_ad_slot = "2373698085";\ngoogle_ad_width = 200;\ngoogle_ad_height = 90;\n//-->\n</script><br />\n<script type="text/javascript"\nsrc="http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js">\n</script>\n</div>\n<ul class="content-list">\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin-example-1/">Quickstart &#8211; default plugin options</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin-example-2/">Create your own demo</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin-example-3/">Static Tabs</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin-example-4/">Inline Sliding Tabs</a></li>\n<li><a href="/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin-example-5/">Using External Links</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>jQuery Social Media Tabs is now available from <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-media-tabs/1932796?ref=designchemical" class="external underline" rel="nofollow">codecanyon</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http